Recipe

=======================
Added:
1. paperclip

remark:

Using 
>rails g paperclip step image 
to generate the migration

Use <% unless step.new_record? %> to check if the step not exist in record.
If you don't have a step record, then rails will create a new step record, therefore, we check by the 'new_record?'

